# WooMU
## WooCommerce MultiSite Fork

WooMU is the first attempt to create an Open Source MultiSite and Multi Store version of the popular eCommerce solution for WordPress, WooCommerceâ„¢.

We are still developing the Alpha version. Come back soon to download the Beta!

In the meantime join our great community and share your ideas with our contributors! http://www.woomu.org

###### WooMU.org it's not affiliated with WooCommerce™ or WooThemes™ in any way. While WooMU will focus on keeping compatibility with future releases of WooCommerce™, WooMU is working on the Open Source WooCommerce™ code to create a <u>distinct</u> Open Source MultiSite version of it.
